  instagram:`INSTAGRAM CAPTION\n\n73% of people who walk through our doors become members.\n\nNot because of a sales pitch.\n\nBecause of this:\n- Free body composition scan on day 1\n- Dedicated coach from day 1\n- Program designed around YOUR goals, not a template\n\nThe assessment is free. The transformation is earned.\n\nBook yours through the link in bio.\n\n#IronTribeFitness #MalvarBatangas #FitnessGym #CoachingGym`,
  campaign:`SOCIAL MEDIA CAMPAIGN — June 2026\n\nCAMPAIGN: "Iron Tribe June Challenge"\nDuration: June 9–30 · Platform: Facebook + Instagram\n\nWEEK 1 (Jun 9–15) — ANNOUNCE:\n· Post 1 (Tue): Iron Month challenge leaderboard reveal\n· Post 2 (Thu): Transformation story — Maria Santos (-6kg)\n· Post 3 (Sat): Community energy recap from Saturday class\n\nWEEK 2 (Jun 16–22) — EDUCATE:\n· Post 4 (Mon): "Why your gym needs a coach, not just equipment"\n· Post 5 (Wed): Coach spotlight — Coach Paolo calisthenics highlight\n· Post 6 (Fri): Member milestone shoutout\n\nWEEK 3 (Jun 23–30) — CONVERT:\n· Post 7 (Mon): Final 30-day challenge enrollment push\n· Post 8 (Wed): July promo preview\n· Post 9 (Sat): Iron Month final leaderboard + prize announcement\n\nCaption tone: Supportive, energetic, community-first.`,
  sms:`SMS CAMPAIGN — June Promo\n\nBatch 1 — New Leads:\n"Hi [Name]! Iron Tribe here. Your free body assessment slot is still open this week. Reply YES to confirm — takes only 30 mins. Malvar, Batangas"\n\nBatch 2 — At-Risk Members:\n"Hey [Name], Coach [X] noticed you have been busy lately. Your slot is saved — come back anytime this week and let us check in on your progress."\n\nBatch 3 — Annual Renewal:\n"Hi [Name]! Your Iron Tribe membership renews this month. Renew now and lock in the current rate + get a free body comp scan. Reply RENEW."`,
};

const AI_OUTPUTS={
