            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style={{display:'grid',gridTemplateColumns:'repeat(3,1fr)',gap:14,marginBottom:40}}>
        {[['Coaching-First','Every member gets a dedicated coach from day one. Not a number — a person with a plan.'],
          ['Evidence-Based','Programs built on what actually works. No fads. No guesswork. Progressive, systematic training.'],
          ['Community','Iron Tribe members stay because of the community. 94% retention — well above industry average.'],
        ].map(([title,desc])=>(
